It's focused on training the impasto painting and can to some extent recreate the portrayal of mature female and males.

Takamichi is well-known for creating cover art for magazines, but he has also been involved in illustrating several visual novels. In particular, "果てしなく青い、この空の下で…。" is a hidden masterpiece.

Usage Tips:

  • Recommended model is AbyssOrangeMix3

  • Use a weight of 0.8 - 1.0

items.name: Rey from Star Wars (Daisy Ridley)
items.description:
This LyCORIS has been trained after carefully selecting 103 images, most of them screenshots from Episode VII movie. All photos have been enhanced to make the most of them.

Many people ask for my workflow. I think that the most important thing is the time I spend looking for really very good pictures. This model have been trained in about 45 minutes but I have spent 8-10 hours looking for and enhancing images, and making captions. It is really a tedious work but I prefer quality over quantity.

When downloading model and testing it, try to copy any of the prompts I have used, and make some variations in order to get other images you prefer. Have fun!

I don't ask for anything but any respectful constructive review (after having tested the model) would be highly appreciated or at least press Like if you're happy with results after trying it out! Thanks in advance and enjoy it!

From my experience it runs best with Edge Of Realism, pirsusEpicRealism, epicDiffusion, RealisticVision, CyberRealistic, Deliberate checkpoints, among others, although I think it will be just fine in other SD 1.5 models as well.

CFG scale should be between 4-7.

LyCORIS weights should be between 0.9-1.2

Notice: This free work is intended for art and illustration purposes of emergent technology and not intended nor' trained for making illicit images, as the author I've taken care to not use any private data in the training process or designed it for such purposes. By downloading this model you are agreeing with the aforementioned intent and that you will not use my work to create / share images of a potentially immoral and / or illegal nature.

items.name: Poppy Drayton
items.description:
A request of @Korma.

Poppy Drayton is a British actress mainly known for her roles in TV shows such as The Shannara Chronicles or Charmed.

140-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (p0ppydrayt0n:0.99), a woman as a movie star, modelshoot style, (extremely detailed CG unity 8k wallpaper), photo of the most beautiful artwork in the world, professional majestic oil painting by Ed Blinkey, Atey Ghailan, Studio Ghibli, by Jeremy Mann, Greg Manchess, Antonio Moro, trending on ArtStation, trending on CGSociety, Intricate, High Detail, Sharp focus, dramatic, photorealistic painting art by midjourney and greg rutkowski, (white turtleneck top:1.2), ((movie premiere)), (long skirt), ((standing near a movie theater)), ((paparazzi in the background)), (looking at viewer:1.2), (detailed pupils:1.3), ((closeup portrait:1.1))"
